OL,3,CNo-one charged in 98% of county's farm
OL,4,Cthefts
OL,6,FLess than 2% of thefts from farms in
OL,7,FLincolnshire in the last five years
OL,8,Fresulted in anyone being charged,
OL,9,Ffigures obtained by ITV Calendar show.
OL,11,FA freedom of information request to
OL,12,FLincolnshire Police showed there were
OL,13,F1,373 reported thefts from farms in
OL,14,Fthe county between 2019 and 2023.
OL,16,FIn the same period, there were just 47
OL,17,Farrests and 19 charges.
OL,19,FHowever, under-reporting means the
OL,20,Ftrue scale of the problem is likely to
OL,21,Fbe much bigger.
