OL,6,FAdam Duguid, who runs Home Farm Dairy
OL,7,Fin at Market Rasen, has had tools and
OL,8,Fmachinery stolen from his premises
OL,9,Fseveral times.
OL,11,F"A truck costs around #20,000, a GPS
OL,12,Fis around #10-#15,000 to replace. But
OL,13,Fthe main impact is not how much it
OL,14,Fcosts to replace," he said.
OL,16,F"It's the downtime you experience -
OL,17,Fyou have to wait months to get a
OL,18,Freplacement for the kit that's been
OL,19,Fstolen. In the intervening time you
OL,20,Fcan't use the equipment you need to do
OL,21,Fyour job."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/8
