OL,6,FOn the same day that Calendar filmed
OL,7,Fwith Mr Duguid, he had a #20,000
OL,8,Ftractor stolen.
OL,10,F"The feeling that someone has broken
OL,11,Fonto your property and taken things
OL,12,Fthat belong to you is very
OL,13,Ffrustrating," he said.
OL,15,FMr Duguid has spent thousands of
OL,16,Fpounds installing CCTV, extra fencing
OL,17,Fand has hired a rapid-response
OL,18,Fsecurity team.
