OL,6,FHe said: "We've installed more fencing
OL,7,Fso they have more physical barriers to
OL,8,Fget through. We have CCTV all over the
OL,9,Ffarm, but people wear balaclavas and
OL,10,Fconceal their faces. They're quite
OL,11,Fbrazen about it."
OL,13,FUnion NFU estimates the cost of rural
OL,14,Fcrime increased by 4.3% year-on-year
OL,15,Fin 2023, to #52.8m, as criminal gangs
OL,16,Fcashed in on continuing high inflation
OL,17,Fand ready resale markets domestically
OL,18,Fand overseas.
