OL,6,FSpeaking in August, vice president
OL,7,FRachel Hallos said: "Rural crime has
OL,8,Fcontinued to plague the British
OL,9,Fcountryside over the past year.
OL,11,F"Criminals steal expensive GPS
OL,12,Fequipment, livestock and high-value
OL,13,Ffarm machinery, while also trespassing
OL,14,Fon private land and regularly fly-
OL,15,Ftipping tons of rubbish.
