OL,6,F"Not only does rural crime
OL,7,Fsignificantly cost the UK on a
OL,8,Fnational level, but it also has a
OL,9,Fsignificant impact personally to those
OL,10,Ffarm businesses and farming families
OL,11,Ffinancially and emotionally affected,
OL,12,Fleaving many rural communities feeling
OL,13,Fvulnerable and intimidated."
OL,15,FLincolnshire Police has a dedicated
OL,16,Frural crime team to police an area of
OL,17,Fmore than 2,500 square miles.
