OL,6,FThey dedicate their time to tackling
OL,7,Fcrimes such as hare coursing and
OL,8,Fwildlife crime, arson, flytipping,
OL,9,Flead theft, theft from farms and rural
OL,10,Fproperties.
OL,12,FInsp Chris Davis, from the team, said:
OL,13,F"We know that rural crime and theft
OL,14,Fhas a huge impact on our farming
OL,15,Fcommunity and we would encourage
OL,16,Fanyone who has been a victim of rural
OL,17,Fcrime to contact Lincolnshire Police.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G7/8
