OL,3,CNo-one charged in 98% of county's farm
OL,4,Cthefts
OL,6,F"We act on intelligence provided by
OL,7,Four communities so the more reports we
OL,8,Fget, we can then work out which areas
OL,9,Fare targeted the most and then deploy
OL,10,Fmore officers in that area.
OL,12,F"Quite a lot of what we do is
OL,13,Fdisruptive. So if we can arrest
OL,14,Fsomeone, detain them and seize their
OL,15,Fvehicles, that can also have an
OL,16,Fimpact. While we might not always get
OL,17,Fcharges, quite often the activities we
OL,18,Fdeal with will stop people committing
OL,19,Ffurther offences."
